OL,3,CPlans to shake up Welsh school year
OL,4,Cshelved for at least four years
OL,6,FPlans to change the school year in
OL,7,FWales have been shelved and will not
OL,8,Ftake place this Senedd term, the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment has announced.
OL,11,FIt follows a mixed response from the
OL,12,Fbiggest Welsh Government education
OL,13,Fconsultation on record.
OL,15,FThe decision on if and when to
OL,16,Fimplement any shake-up will be
OL,17,Fdeferred to the next Senedd term to
OL,18,Fallow schools to deliver other reforms
OL,19,Fand improve attainment.
