OL,3,CPlans to shake up Welsh school year
OL,4,Cshelved for at least four years
OL,6,FThe consultation generated more than
OL,7,F16,000 responses, which sought views
OL,8,Fon to spread school holidays out more
OL,9,Fevenly across the year.
OL,11,FProposals suggested moving a week from
OL,12,Fthe start of the summer break into the
OL,13,Fautumn break, creating a two-week half
OL,14,Fterm.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Government has said the
OL,17,Fproposal was to improve the education
OL,18,Fexperiences of young people,
OL,19,Fespecially the most disadvantaged, and
OL,20,Falign more effectively with how
OL,21,Ffamilies live and work.
