OL,6,FThe pause will also allow other
OL,7,Freforms like the new curriculum for
OL,8,FWales and reforms of Additional
OL,9,FLearning Needs provision to be fully
OL,10,Fimplemented and rolled out before
OL,11,Fother changes are introduced.
OL,13,FIf the plans are looked at again, they
OL,14,Fwould unlikely be implemented before
OL,15,FSeptember 2028.
