OL,6,FLynne Neagle, the Welsh Government's
OL,7,Feducation secretary, said: "My
OL,8,Fstarting point is always the best
OL,9,Finterests of children and young
OL,10,Fpeople. This means ensuring reforms
OL,11,Fare properly planned out and have the
OL,12,Ftime and space to succeed.
OL,14,F"Opinion was hugely divided on this.
OL,15,FTo ensure we get this right, we need
OL,16,Fto continue listening to and engaging
OL,17,Fwith schools, teachers, unions as well
OL,18,Fas children, young people and parents
OL,19,Fon how best we can implement any
OL,20,Fchanges in the future.
