OL,3,CPlans to shake up Welsh school year
OL,4,Cshelved for at least four years
OL,6,FWelsh Conservatives' shadow education
OL,7,Fminister Tom Giffard MS said:
OL,8,F"Education in Wales is in crisis with
OL,9,Fsoaring absenteeism, a shocking
OL,10,Fdecline in education standards, the
OL,11,Fworst PISA results in the UK and
OL,12,Frising incidences of violence plaguing
OL,13,Four schools.
OL,15,F"We have long called for the Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment to scrap this distraction
OL,17,Fand get on with tackling the problems
OL,18,Fthey have created in education over
OL,19,Fthe past 25 years.
