OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"The total cost of the work around the
OL,8,Fstructure of the school year is
OL,9,Fapproximately #350,000. This included
OL,10,Fthe consultation on the school year
OL,11,Fitself, two other pieces of work with
OL,12,FBeaufort Research and Miller Research
OL,13,Fand internal research. All costs were
OL,14,Fbudgeted for as part of the Programme
OL,15,Ffor Government and subsequently, the
OL,16,FCo-operation Agreement."
